{"tid":1838702,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"根本醫護罷工都唔駛怕秋後算賬","createTime":"2020-01-24T06:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T08:05:10.000Z","uid":302191,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d859069522a023a1b9c8187b5a32ce39d2d45b01","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:22:09.000Z","msg":"根本一直以嚟醫護人手都係處於短缺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">供不應求</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算依刻即時罷工都唔會有咩問題<br />\n一嚟政府冇採取任何措施<br />\n一直放啲大陸人落嚟睇醫生<br />\n就算你識多重分身都唔會醫得哂<br />\n再講醫護本身係一個專門嘅職業嚟<br />\n普通人冇可能輕易取代到你哋嘅位置同職位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺人手短缺下 如果佢仲夠膽炒人<br />\n咪變咗高層自己落手做<br />\n你估佢哋有冇咁笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上依家你做好你嘅職責<br />\n政府都唔會覺得你哋出咗好多力<br />\n加人工 加畀黑警都未輪到你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n反而你一個唔好彩感染到的話<br />\n即時畀人隔離 你自己拎條命出嚟 政府當你Condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔講政治 為自己 為健康 都應該<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即時罷工</span></span></strong><br />\n相信係香港人都會支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dcc3ddef99e9c8a87ff8a5b4fd59ea5b34fe2ce","tid":1838702,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:22:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"b48f8278f23881934bb233c6e74c5bb3af1c9515","tid":1838702,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"62bb4ad218e1a850daaa5230104ee25210deb8d5","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"bd428467f9e89c2f0ce0d04e1a7a6d87d7a9f8d9","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:45:40.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"03cbcdbeca63b9eb5cf8645ae810dffd14700c20","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"e365f12f5cf4d52bdab1e2d39ae88259ace90968","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T07:54:52.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"d4a56cd1d9b5f50b08723218d038aa70bfdf13a8","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"時"},{"pid":"e4d902cf604566a4ad4a212528795f0c8251dabc","tid":1838702,"uid":302191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T08:05:10.000Z","msg":"代"}]}